text: FIFA Soccer 96 is a 1995 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts' FIFA series published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the PlayStation, Sega Saturn, Mega Drive, Sega 32X, Game Gear, Super Nintendo, Game Boy and Microsoft Windows.
